   <S PAR='237' RSNT='1' SNO='237'>The matter is decided.</S>
   <S PAR='238' RSNT='1' SNO='238'>I do not care if others think that it is hopeful or hopeless any longer.</S>
   <S PAR='239' RSNT='1' SNO='239'>He has said himself that he will bear all the responsibilities.</S>
   <S PAR='240' RSNT='1' SNO='240'>I can live now in peace.</S>
   <S PAR='241' RSNT='1' SNO='241'>Are not many believers like this poor man?</S>
   <S PAR='242' RSNT='1' SNO='242'>What a pity that many children of God listen to others talk and to their own feeling; they are drifting back and forth.</S>
   <S PAR='243' RSNT='1' SNO='243'>The poor man was assured once he had a word from his friend.</S>
   <S PAR='244' RSNT='1' SNO='244'>The children of God are likewise assured when they have the Word of God.</S>
