   <S PAR='281' RSNT='1' SNO='281'>When He died, He proclaimed, It is finished!</S>
   <S PAR='282' RSNT='1' SNO='282'>John 19:30 .</S>
   <S PAR='283' RSNT='1' SNO='283'>How precious is this word!</S>
   <S PAR='284' RSNT='1' SNO='284'>O Lord!</S>
   <S PAR='285' RSNT='1' SNO='285'>I can never thank You enough for Your great grace!</S>
   <S PAR='286' RSNT='1' SNO='286'>To believe in the Lord Jesus means nothing other than a willingness on the part of us, the helpless and destitute sinners, to be saved by Him.</S>
