   <S PAR='291' RSNT='1' SNO='291'>Praise God, for Christ is faithful and trustworthy.</S>
   <S PAR='292' RSNT='1' SNO='292'>There is no guile found in His mouth!</S>
   <S PAR='293' RSNT='1' SNO='293'>He will never cast out those who come to Him.</S>
