   <S PAR='308' RSNT='1' SNO='308'>This is only a hypothesis.</S>
   <S PAR='309' RSNT='1' SNO='309'>Many people think that if they know that they are saved, they will still want to sin.</S>
   <S PAR='310' RSNT='1' SNO='310'>But this is only a hypothesis.</S>
   <S PAR='311' RSNT='1' SNO='311'>In reality, something exactly opposite happens.</S>
   <S PAR='312' RSNT='1' SNO='312'>If a man knows that he is saved, he will not want to sin anymore, and he will also bear heavenly characteristics in his thought and conduct.</S>
   <S PAR='313' RSNT='1' SNO='313'>I can give you an illustration here.</S>
   <S PAR='314' RSNT='1' SNO='314'>Today in China we are sending a few hundred people to study abroad every year.</S>
