   <S PAR='328' RSNT='1' SNO='328'>When he walks, he should walk like the Americans walk.</S>
   <S PAR='329' RSNT='1' SNO='329'>He should pursue after American fashion in his dress and attire.</S>
   <S PAR='330' RSNT='1' SNO='330'>In other words, all those who are about to go to America have a natural tendency to act and move like an American.</S>
   <S PAR='331' RSNT='1' SNO='331'>If a believer realizes that he has eternal life already, and is a citizen of heaven, he will surely learn the heavenly pattern in everything, in word, conduct, and walk.</S>
   <S PAR='332' RSNT='1' SNO='332'>Those who do not know that they are saved will imitate the world and try to be conformed to it.</S>
   <S PAR='333' RSNT='1' SNO='333'>Brothers, there is no danger of sinning carelessly for those who know that they are saved.</S>
