   <S PAR='335' RSNT='1' SNO='335'>This can be fully confirmed by the spiritual experiences of the believers.</S>
   <S PAR='336' RSNT='1' SNO='336'>Just like those who are going to America try to be Americans, those who are going heavenward will surely learn to be heavenly persons.</S>
   <S PAR='337' RSNT='1' SNO='337'>Dear brothers!</S>
   <S PAR='338' RSNT='1' SNO='338'>You have believed in the Lord Jesus Christ already.</S>
   <S PAR='339' RSNT='1' SNO='339'>This is the most important thing on earth.</S>
