   <S PAR='352' RSNT='1' SNO='352'>We know that we cannot save ourselves.</S>
   <S PAR='353' RSNT='1' SNO='353'>As a result, all the authority, riches, wisdom, power, honor, glory, and praise be unto the slain Lamb for now and evermore!</S>
