   <S PAR='355' RSNT='1' SNO='355'>Since He has loved us and saved us, we should love Him out of a sense of gratitude and should live as saved persons on earth.</S>
   <S PAR='356' RSNT='1' SNO='356'>Since He has begun the good work in our heart, He will surely complete this work until the day of Christ Jesus Phil 1:6 .</S>
   <S PAR='357' RSNT='1' SNO='357'>We cannot please Him by ourselves, because those who are in the flesh cannot please God Rom 8:8 .</S>
